wheat farmers have seen prices drop sharply 
from a year or two ago and a new supplyanddemand report by the 
agriculture department doesnt find much improvement in sight 
overall 199091 global wheat production forecasts increased 
from a month ago with gains in canada china and mexico more than 
offsetting reduced prospects in brazil the european community and 
south africa 
