belonged to iraq was one reason for iraqs aug 2 invasion of the 
emirate 
iraq also wants a deepwater port which it was unable to win 
during the 19801988 iraniraq war 
baghdad had asked kuwait for a 99year lease on two uninhabited 
islands at the mouth of the shattalarab waterway from kuwait 
which would give it control over access to the passage forming the 
border between iran and iraq 
kuwait declined to lease the islands to iraq the day before the 
invasion 
