calming his fears about the steadfastness of us support for 
israel despite recent strains over the new us alliances with 
arab states aligned against iraq 
the meeting will enhance the special relationshi between the 
united states and israel shamir told reporters at the white 
house 
shamir said his meeting with bush convinced him the 
administration doesnt favor an international conference 
the administration has been fighting a proposed resolution at 
the un security council calling for such a conference mainly to 
avoid linking the israelipalestinian dispute with the usled 
drive to force iraq to leave kuwait 
