being part of an interesting process aimed at bringing the 
angolan conflict to a peaceful conclusion 
savimbi made his appearance at the embassy shortly after van 
dunem conferred for about 45 minutes with shevardnadze 
the two meetings represented the most dramatic evidence yet of 
moscow and washington setting aside differences over angola to 
promote national reconciliation in the african country 
