equals 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
the economy is weak its a dismal holiday season for retailers 
and bob and susan rabascho braved three hours on the freeway from 
san diego just to go to a discount home furnishing store in 
burbank calif 
they had to wait another hour to get inside the ikea store but 
they didnt care nor have other shoppers who have mobbed the 
110room store since it opened last month 
the swedenbased ikea is a rare southern california retailing 
success story at a time when sagging real estate prices and layoffs 
in aerospace and construction have put the brakes on spending 
so many people have gone there that burbank police have assigned 
29 officers to handle the traffic jams that followed the stores 3 
million advertising campaign 
things got so bad that cars on the burbank boulevard offramp 
backed up on the golden state freeway police finally implored the 
state transportation department to put a sign on the freeway 
directing drivers to another exit 
after the rabaschos finally made it inside they spent six hours 
and about 200 at ikea the store features assembleityourself 
furniture and offers amenities such as supervised childcare and 
free diapers to keep families happy while they shop 
