tales this year mary muir director of the state employment and 
training office in woburn mass said she sees more young 
unemployed people these days 
for many of these people its the first time theyve been 
unemployed she said its a shock to them 
ryan said initially he didnt think he would have much trouble 
dealing with unemployment but he has had to let some bills slide 
and he receives help from his family 
and with no luck so far in finding a new job ryan said hes had 
trouble getting into the holiday spirit 
